{"tid":2079726,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際線進化　不是隨便得罪人　不是擦鞋　是sell plan make deal","createTime":"2020-06-26T03:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T03:43:12.000Z","uid":261647,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"662dc0c3ca9a19b2652ee1f3a47529b7212a39d2","tid":2079726,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158325452272357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10158325452272357&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SqWONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=645cfd87\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158325452272357</a><br />\n<br />\n外交當然不要隨便得罪人，但同時也不是擦鞋，純粹討好人，擦鞋，並不是外交而只是聯誼。你要外交，就是拿出一個合理的分析和計劃出來，看對方是否接受，而你手上的人力物力與籌碼可以令你有更多的計劃選擇，和更有說服力。<br />\n<br />\n並不是找外國人參加一個公開的場合，對著他們演說一次，你就是在外交，那只是一個聯誼節目。不足以改變任何外交態度與政策，而外交態度與政策，也不是那些討好能夠改變的，如果一個國家的外交純粹取決於個別政黨與人員的好感與感性，而不是戰略利弊，那國家不會生存太久。<br />\n<br />\n外交是 make deal with them，你先要有 deal 才有外交。"},{"pid":"ae19eda055420cc5e2566ad6964023b8464b21e0","tid":2079726,"uid":54415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:40:47.000Z","msg":"樓主寫得唔錯<br />\n外交係deal唔係扮慘做乞兒<br />\n咩人情都好，要有利益先得"},{"pid":"2c4852b6d649303ef1ef7f2f4504bea75762e69a","tid":2079726,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c003faef348c1535b215d6a43ed57094932e2c9c","tid":2079726,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7CNJoXi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7CNJoXi.png&h=2d088d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1eGBJXm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1eGBJXm.png&h=cc054f75&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}